@1004633 = ~Ha!  I wish that were possible.  The southern pass has long since been snowed-in by this damnable weather we've been having lately.  Now I hear tell that even the northern route to the Ten-Towns has been blocked by an avalanche.  Mark my words; none of us will last through this winter.  We're all done for.~ []
