@1014810 = ~Upon closer look at this suit of plate mail, its metal seems to be in a corporeal state, hence its shadowed look.  Upon it being worn, it will make the wearer appear as shadowed as the armor is.  It will also provide extra protection against missile weapons while the wearer is in its shadowed state.

