 Thief~ []
@1016295 = ~The simplest and humblest of staff weapons, the quarterstaff is a length of wood ranging six to nine feet in length.  High quality quarterstaffs are made of stout oak and are shod with metal at both ends.  The quarterstaff must be wielded with both hands.

STATISTICS:

