@1023799 = ~The use of magic causes a collection of magical residue around the caster.  It is this residue which prevents even the most skilled of casters from casting spells in quick succession.

Daer'Ragh's Aura Cleaning removes the residue of spell casting as the next spell casting begins.  This allows a greatly increased rate of spell casting.~ []
@1025876 = ~Stoneskin (Alteration)
