@4424386 = ~This fiery armor is actually a demon manifested into the physical embodiment of infernal defense.  The breastplate of the armor bears a malefic face, and the entire assembly looks impossibly wicked and meticulously sculpted.  The armor is warm to the touch, and it is obviously supernatural.

STATISTICS:

Armor Class: 1
Weight: 45
Special:  
 Resist Cold: Set to 100%
